features: Asymmetrical Construction - Features a large capacity in vintage style. An asymmetrical construction with a sense of industrial beauty allows you to store items of varying sizes. Rustic brown color compliments with homes, offices, coffee shops and other stores of different decoration styles.

Sturdy & Durable - Processed out of premium eco-friendly particleboard and high quality iron frame. Panels meet U.S. CARB (California Air Resource Board) requirements and each performs excellently in resisting scratches and stains, easy to clean and durable. The combination of wooden shelves and iron frame not only ensures good stability and durability, but also provides a safe environment for your home office or bedroom. (Each shelf is sturdy enough to hold 50 lbs.)

Extra Large Storage Space - This gorgeous bookshelf features and oversize of 39 × 11.7 × 70.5 in (100 × 30 × 180 cm) and 6 open shelves (tier height 12.6 ~ 26 in). asymmetrical design ensures ample space for sorting and storing your items of varying heights: books: framed photos, pottery, collections, or potted plants.

Multiple Purposes - It is not just a bookshelf, but a spacious shelf serving as a display shelf, storage shelf, or floor screen in your living room, kitchen, or balcony. It is a good organizer for your home.

Easy to Assemble - Each component part is clearly labeled. Simple construction and detailed instructions allow you to finish assembling it in 15 ~ 20 minutes. If you come across any problems during assembly, please feel free to tell our Customer Service for immediate and professional solutions.
body.description: Asymmetrical Construction 6 Open Shelves Our bookshelf is constructed by P2 grade particleboard and premium iron frame. Sturdy construction, together with elegant design, makes your home organized and you happy. We believe such a bookshelf fits in any place in your house, like your living room, kitchen, balcony, etc. It is elegant, practical, easy to clean and assemble. Adjustable foot pads at the bottom not only prevent it from slipping and protect it against scratches, but also keep it stable and horizontal.
